  "texts": [
    "To avoid data copy and enable direct access to the pages of the matrix, Guest Physical Addresses (GPAs) in the matrix are translated into Host Virtual Addresses (HVAs) using several threads to accelerate the translation and then improve the overall performance.",
    "After the deserialization, the system proceeds with data operations on the DPUs.",
    "vPIM employs 8 threads to execute operations.",
    "This choice aligns with the system's setup, which involves 64 DPUs organized into chips of 8 DPUs.",
    "Consequently, operations are performed on 8 DPUs at a time."
  ],
